{"tid":1534563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好想知勇武比人拉曬之後和理非們會唔會企出黎","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:13:01.000Z","uid":121866,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"924fd74bf2e55fd3cd475184b2962571a17c1447","tid":1534563,"uid":121866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"以而家呢個打壓力度同速度<br />\n前線手足既人手同裝備都差不多耗盡<br />\n<br />\n或者林鄭係正確 搞事既只係一少撮人<br />\n只需要拉晒佢地 打撚傷晒佢地 基本上香港就回復平靜<br />\n以後香港都冇人再敢企出黎反抗<br />\n<br />\n我地真係好驚 我地驚既唔係自己既身驅被打傷 唔係驚被拉被殺<br />\n而係驚我地呢套理念會被消滅 <br />\n<br />\nWe are told to remember the idea, not the man, because a man can fail. He can be caught, he can be killed and forgotten, but 400 years later, an idea can still change the world.<br />\n<br />\n我只係想問問大家 會否帶上面罩 為呢套理念而戰"},{"pid":"0295b0eeed18cc02ad3ebf1a705fe403ee28770c","tid":1534563,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61e819231010e3bf69af402a24d72b8402680e54","tid":1534563,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔少人六月第一次遊行後，愈企愈前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c919860a5563a5db7dd221de6e2aa86594a3c9f0","tid":1534563,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"c8e8596b0e5a65bfc55ef58413d6f816e63b302e","tid":1534563,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"3d2fe6068c05612523162c22d5e5578e0892b12c","tid":1534563,"uid":40223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d337416e5380e51a11d6b3a112df58c60eae7540","tid":1534563,"uid":121866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2fe6068c05612523162c22d5e5578e0892b12c","tid":1534563,"uid":40223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"明白"},{"pid":"6e8393da956f5d21ebaedb611f7b60a5b08534f7","tid":1534563,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"我體力差，企唔到最前線衝<br />\n但只要我一日企到出黎，我都會繼續出黎"},{"pid":"b71fea11e1639649a9055c6e216957dfa7231770","tid":1534563,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n之前睇到12歲小朋友被拉已經好心痛<br />\n開學日見到中學生叫口號叫到大大聲忍唔住喊左<br />\n<br />\n多謝小朋友俾我勇氣<br />\n對唔住勇武，我好細膽所以只敢買gear課金<br />\n<br />\n不完美，會改善<br />\n今後起，會繼續行前"},{"pid":"a03ef12ffd46126af49e3490117f057ca1fb161d","tid":1534563,"uid":277144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"冇錢？籌啦！即科水"}]}